item.title: CVE-2016-9044|2024-08-06T02:42:09.433Z -- information%20builders -- webfocus
item.description: An exploitable command execution vulnerability exists in Information Builders WebFOCUS Business Intelligence Portal 8.1 . A specially crafted web parameter can cause a command injection. An authenticated attacker can send a crafted web request to trigger this vulnerability.
